 & =\left.\frac{\partial h}{\partial q_{d}}\right|_{\left(q_{d},\dot{q}_{d}\right)}\dot{q}_{d}+\left.\frac{\partial h}{\partial\dot{q}_{d}}\right|_{\left(q_{d},\dot{q}_{d}\right)}\ddot{q}_{d}-\left.\frac{\partial f}{\partial q}\right|_{\left(q,\dot{q}\right)}\dot{q}-\left.\frac{\partial f}{\partial\dot{q}}\right|_{\left(q,\dot{q}\right)}\ddot{q}-\dot{u}-\dot{d}\left(t\right)+k_{1}\dot{r}_{1}-k_{1}^{2}\dot{e}+k_{2}\dot{r}_{1}\\
