 & +\intop_{t_{0}}^{t}\left(K_{\text{RISE}}\text{sgn}\left(r_{1}\left(\tau\right)\right)+\Phi\left(\kappa\left(\tau\right),\hat{\theta}\left(\tau\right)\right)+\left(k_{1}k_{2}k_{3}+k_{1}\right)e\left(\tau\right)\right)d\tau
